value: Je ne vous laisserai pas faire !
Je dois protéger tout le monde !
Does this Askran garb suit me?
Wah! You surprised me. Is something...askew? Thanks for fixing it!
Il me reste tant à apprendre sur Askr. Pouvez-vous m'aider ?
I wonder what Caeda will think of these clothes...
I plan to venture out of the castle today. Would you join me in town? I want to find out more about Askr.

Je viens peut-être d'un autre monde, mais mon devoir reste le
même : je dois protéger ceux qui ne peuvent pas le faire eux-mêmes.
You seem really pleased that I'm dressed like this. I had no idea you'd all enjoy seeing me in Askran garb!
